{"thig6.8:0.1":"Therigatha 6.8 ","thig6.8:0.2":"Chakkanipata ","thig6.8:0.3":"Vijayatherigatha ","thig6.8:1.1":"“Catukkhattum pancakkhattum, ","thig6.8:1.2":"vihara upanikkhamim; ","thig6.8:1.3":"Aladdha cetaso santim, ","thig6.8:1.4":"citte avasavattini. ","thig6.8:2.1":"Bhikkhunim upasankamma, ","thig6.8:2.2":"sakkaccam paripucchaham; ","thig6.8:2.3":"Sa me dhammamadesesi, ","thig6.8:2.4":"dhatuayatanani ca. ","thig6.8:3.1":"Cattari ariyasaccani, ","thig6.8:3.2":"indriyani balani ca; ","thig6.8:3.3":"Bojjhangatthangikam maggam, ","thig6.8:3.4":"uttamatthassa pattiya. ","thig6.8:4.1":"Tassaham vacanam sutva, ","thig6.8:4.2":"karonti anusasanim; ","thig6.8:4.3":"Rattiya purime yame, ","thig6.8:4.4":"pubbajatimanussarim. ","thig6.8:5.1":"Rattiya majjhime yame, ","thig6.8:5.2":"dibbacakkhum visodhayim; ","thig6.8:5.3":"Rattiya pacchime yame, ","thig6.8:5.4":"tamokhandham padalayim. ","thig6.8:6.1":"Pitisukhena ca kayam, ","thig6.8:6.2":"Pharitva viharim tada; ","thig6.8:6.3":"Sattamiya pade pasaresim, ","thig6.8:6.4":"Tamokhandham padaliya”ti. ","thig6.8:7.1":"… Vijaya theri …. ","thig6.8:8.1":"Chakkanipato nitthito. "}